-- Lufthansa Freighter Crashes in Saudi Arabia, No Casualties, Saudi TV Says
-- Inal Ersan
-- 2010-07-27T09:29:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/lufthansa-freighter-crashes-in-saudi-arabia-no-casualties-saudi-tv-says.html

          
          
             A cargo aircraft owned by Deutsche
Lufthansa AG crashed at an airport in the Saudi capital Riyadh
today, the Saudi state television reported.  
 It said there were no reports of casualties at the King
Khaled International Airport. It did not give further details.  
